{
  "book": 19,
  "chapter": 78,
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "heading": "神與他的子民"
    },
    {
      "type": "desc",
      "contents": []
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Give ear, O my people, to my law; Incline your ears to the words of my mouth. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Give ear, O my people, to my law; Incline your ears to the words of my mouth."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "I will open my mouth in a parable; I will utter dark sayings of old, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "I will open my mouth in a parable; I will utter dark sayings of old,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Which we have heard and known, And our fathers have told us. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Which we have heard and known, And our fathers have told us."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "We will not hide them from their children, Telling to the generation to come the praises of the Lord, And His strength and His wonderful works that He has done. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We will not hide them from their children, Telling to the generation to come the praises of the Lord, And His strength and His wonderful works that He has done."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We will not hide them from their children, Telling to the generation to come the praises of the Lord, And His strength and His wonderful works that He has done."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For He established a testimony in Jacob, And appointed a law in Israel, Which He commanded our fathers, That they should make them known to their children; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For He established a testimony in Jacob, And appointed a law in Israel, Which He commanded our fathers, That they should make them known to their children;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For He established a testimony in Jacob, And appointed a law in Israel, Which He commanded our fathers, That they should make them known to their children;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "That the generation to come might know them, The children who would be born, That they may arise and declare them to their children, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "That the generation to come might know them, The children who would be born, That they may arise and declare them to their children,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "That they may set their hope in God, And not forget the works of God, But keep His commandments; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "That they may set their hope in God, And not forget the works of God, But keep His commandments;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "That they may set their hope in God, And not forget the works of God, But keep His commandments;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And may not be like their fathers, A stubborn and rebellious generation, A generation that did not set its heart aright, And whose spirit was not faithful to God. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And may not be like their fathers, A stubborn and rebellious generation, A generation that did not set its heart aright, And whose spirit was not faithful to God."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And may not be like their fathers, A stubborn and rebellious generation, A generation that did not set its heart aright, And whose spirit was not faithful to God."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The children of Ephraim, being armed and carrying bows, Turned back in the day of battle. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The children of Ephraim, being armed and carrying bows, Turned back in the day of battle."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They did not keep the covenant of God; They refused to walk in His law, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They did not keep the covenant of God; They refused to walk in His law,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And forgot His works And His wonders that He had shown them. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And forgot His works And His wonders that He had shown them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Marvelous things He did in the sight of their fathers, In the land of Egypt, in the field of Zoan. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Marvelous things He did in the sight of their fathers, In the land of Egypt, in the field of Zoan."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He divided the sea and caused them to pass through; And He made the waters stand up like a heap. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He divided the sea and caused them to pass through; And He made the waters stand up like a heap."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "In the daytime also He led them with the cloud, And all the night with a light of fire. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "In the daytime also He led them with the cloud, And all the night with a light of fire."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He split the rocks in the wilderness, And gave them drink in abundance like the depths. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He split the rocks in the wilderness, And gave them drink in abundance like the depths."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He also brought streams out of the rock, And caused waters to run down like rivers. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He also brought streams out of the rock, And caused waters to run down like rivers."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But they sinned even more against Him By rebelling against the Most High in the wilderness. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But they sinned even more against Him By rebelling against the Most High in the wilderness."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And they tested God in their heart By asking for the food of their fancy. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And they tested God in their heart By asking for the food of their fancy."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Yes, they spoke against God: They said, “Can God prepare a table in the wilderness? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Yes, they spoke against God: They said, “Can God prepare a table in the wilderness?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Behold, He struck the rock, So that the waters gushed out, And the streams overflowed. Can He give bread also? Can He provide meat for His people?” "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Behold, He struck the rock, So that the waters gushed out, And the streams overflowed. Can He give bread also? Can He provide meat for His people?”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Behold, He struck the rock, So that the waters gushed out, And the streams overflowed. Can He give bread also? Can He provide meat for His people?”"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Therefore the Lord heard this and was furious; So a fire was kindled against Jacob, And anger also came up against Israel, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Therefore the Lord heard this and was furious; So a fire was kindled against Jacob, And anger also came up against Israel,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Therefore the Lord heard this and was furious; So a fire was kindled against Jacob, And anger also came up against Israel,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Because they did not believe in God, And did not trust in His salvation. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Because they did not believe in God, And did not trust in His salvation."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Yet He had commanded the clouds above, And opened the doors of heaven, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Yet He had commanded the clouds above, And opened the doors of heaven,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 23,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Had rained down manna on them to eat, And given them of the bread of heaven. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Had rained down manna on them to eat, And given them of the bread of heaven."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 24,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Men ate angels’ food; He sent them food to the full. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Men ate angels’ food; He sent them food to the full."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 25,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He caused an east wind to blow in the heavens; And by His power He brought in the south wind. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He caused an east wind to blow in the heavens; And by His power He brought in the south wind."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 26,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He also rained meat on them like the dust, Feathered fowl like the sand of the seas; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He also rained meat on them like the dust, Feathered fowl like the sand of the seas;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 27,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And He let them fall in the midst of their camp, All around their dwellings. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And He let them fall in the midst of their camp, All around their dwellings."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 28,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "So they ate and were well filled, For He gave them their own desire. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "So they ate and were well filled, For He gave them their own desire."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 29,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They were not deprived of their craving; But while their food was still in their mouths, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They were not deprived of their craving; But while their food was still in their mouths,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 30,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The wrath of God came against them, And slew the stoutest of them, And struck down the choice men of Israel. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The wrath of God came against them, And slew the stoutest of them, And struck down the choice men of Israel."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The wrath of God came against them, And slew the stoutest of them, And struck down the choice men of Israel."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 31,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "In spite of this they still sinned, And did not believe in His wondrous works. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "In spite of this they still sinned, And did not believe in His wondrous works."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 32,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Therefore their days He consumed in futility, And their years in fear. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Therefore their days He consumed in futility, And their years in fear."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 33,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When He slew them, then they sought Him; And they returned and sought earnestly for God. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When He slew them, then they sought Him; And they returned and sought earnestly for God."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 34,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 35,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Then they remembered that God was their rock, And the Most High God their Redeemer. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 35,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Then they remembered that God was their rock, And the Most High God their Redeemer."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 35,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 36,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Nevertheless they flattered Him with their mouth, And they lied to Him with their tongue; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 36,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Nevertheless they flattered Him with their mouth, And they lied to Him with their tongue;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 36,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 37,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For their heart was not steadfast with Him, Nor were they faithful in His covenant. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 37,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For their heart was not steadfast with Him, Nor were they faithful in His covenant."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 37,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But He, being full of compassion, forgave their iniquity, And did not destroy them. Yes, many a time He turned His anger away, And did not stir up all His wrath; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But He, being full of compassion, forgave their iniquity, And did not destroy them. Yes, many a time He turned His anger away, And did not stir up all His wrath;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But He, being full of compassion, forgave their iniquity, And did not destroy them. Yes, many a time He turned His anger away, And did not stir up all His wrath;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But He, being full of compassion, forgave their iniquity, And did not destroy them. Yes, many a time He turned His anger away, And did not stir up all His wrath;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But He, being full of compassion, forgave their iniquity, And did not destroy them. Yes, many a time He turned His anger away, And did not stir up all His wrath;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 38,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 39,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For He remembered that they were  but flesh, A breath that passes away and does not come again. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 39,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For He remembered that they were  but flesh, A breath that passes away and does not come again."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 39,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 40,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "How often they provoked Him in the wilderness, And grieved Him in the desert! "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 40,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "How often they provoked Him in the wilderness, And grieved Him in the desert!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 40,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 41,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Yes, again and again they tempted God, And limited the Holy One of Israel. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 41,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Yes, again and again they tempted God, And limited the Holy One of Israel."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 41,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 42,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "They did not remember His power: The day when He redeemed them from the enemy, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 42,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "They did not remember His power: The day when He redeemed them from the enemy,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 42,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 43,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When He worked His signs in Egypt, And His wonders in the field of Zoan; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 43,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When He worked His signs in Egypt, And His wonders in the field of Zoan;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 43,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 44,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Turned their rivers into blood, And their streams, that they could not drink. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 44,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Turned their rivers into blood, And their streams, that they could not drink."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 44,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 45,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He sent swarms of flies among them, which devoured them, And frogs, which destroyed them. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 45,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He sent swarms of flies among them, which devoured them, And frogs, which destroyed them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 45,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 46,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He also gave their crops to the caterpillar, And their labor to the locust. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 46,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He also gave their crops to the caterpillar, And their labor to the locust."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 46,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 47,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He destroyed their vines with hail, And their sycamore trees with frost. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 47,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He destroyed their vines with hail, And their sycamore trees with frost."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 47,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 48,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He also gave up their cattle to the hail, And their flocks to fiery lightning. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 48,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He also gave up their cattle to the hail, And their flocks to fiery lightning."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 48,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 49,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He cast on them the fierceness of His anger, Wrath, indignation, and trouble, By sending angels of destruction among  them. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 49,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He cast on them the fierceness of His anger, Wrath, indignation, and trouble, By sending angels of destruction among  them."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 49,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 50,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He made a path for His anger; He did not spare their soul from death, But gave their life over to the plague, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 50,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He made a path for His anger; He did not spare their soul from death, But gave their life over to the plague,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 50,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He made a path for His anger; He did not spare their soul from death, But gave their life over to the plague,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 50,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 51,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And destroyed all the firstborn in Egypt, The first of their strength in the tents of Ham. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 51,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And destroyed all the firstborn in Egypt, The first of their strength in the tents of Ham."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 51,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 52,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But He made His own people go forth like sheep, And guided them in the wilderness like a flock; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 52,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But He made His own people go forth like sheep, And guided them in the wilderness like a flock;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 52,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 53,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And He led them on safely, so that they did not fear; But the sea overwhelmed their enemies. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 53,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And He led them on safely, so that they did not fear; But the sea overwhelmed their enemies."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 53,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 54,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And He brought them to His holy border, This mountain which His right hand had acquired. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 54,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And He brought them to His holy border, This mountain which His right hand had acquired."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 54,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 55,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He also drove out the nations before them, Allotted them an inheritance by survey, And made the tribes of Israel dwell in their tents. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 55,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He also drove out the nations before them, Allotted them an inheritance by survey, And made the tribes of Israel dwell in their tents."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 55,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He also drove out the nations before them, Allotted them an inheritance by survey, And made the tribes of Israel dwell in their tents."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 55,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 56,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Yet they tested and provoked the Most High God, And did not keep His testimonies, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 56,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Yet they tested and provoked the Most High God, And did not keep His testimonies,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 56,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 57,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But turned back and acted unfaithfully like their fathers; They were turned aside like a deceitful bow. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 57,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But turned back and acted unfaithfully like their fathers; They were turned aside like a deceitful bow."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 57,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 58,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For they provoked Him to anger with their high places, And moved Him to jealousy with their carved images. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 58,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For they provoked Him to anger with their high places, And moved Him to jealousy with their carved images."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 58,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 59,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "When God heard this, He was furious, And greatly abhorred Israel, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 59,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "When God heard this, He was furious, And greatly abhorred Israel,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 59,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 60,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "So that He forsook the tabernacle of Shiloh, The tent He had placed among men, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 60,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "So that He forsook the tabernacle of Shiloh, The tent He had placed among men,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 60,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 61,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And delivered His strength into captivity, And His glory into the enemy’s hand. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 61,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And delivered His strength into captivity, And His glory into the enemy’s hand."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 61,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 62,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He also gave His people over to the sword, And was furious with His inheritance. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 62,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He also gave His people over to the sword, And was furious with His inheritance."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 62,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 63,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The fire consumed their young men, And their maidens were not given in marriage. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 63,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The fire consumed their young men, And their maidens were not given in marriage."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 63,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 64,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Their priests fell by the sword, And their widows made no lamentation. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 64,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Their priests fell by the sword, And their widows made no lamentation."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 64,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 65,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Then the Lord awoke as from sleep, Like a mighty man who shouts because of wine. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 65,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Then the Lord awoke as from sleep, Like a mighty man who shouts because of wine."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 65,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 66,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And He beat back His enemies; He put them to a perpetual reproach. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 66,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And He beat back His enemies; He put them to a perpetual reproach."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 66,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 67,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Moreover He rejected the tent of Joseph, And did not choose the tribe of Ephraim, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 67,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Moreover He rejected the tent of Joseph, And did not choose the tribe of Ephraim,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 67,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 68,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But chose the tribe of Judah, Mount Zion which He loved. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 68,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 69,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "And He built His sanctuary like the heights, Like the earth which He has established forever. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 69,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "And He built His sanctuary like the heights, Like the earth which He has established forever."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 69,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 70,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "He also chose David His servant, And took him from the sheepfolds; "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 70,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "He also chose David His servant, And took him from the sheepfolds;"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 70,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 71,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "From following the ewes that had young He brought him, To shepherd Jacob His people, And Israel His inheritance. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 71,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "From following the ewes that had young He brought him, To shepherd Jacob His people, And Israel His inheritance."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 71,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "From following the ewes that had young He brought him, To shepherd Jacob His people, And Israel His inheritance."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 71,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 72,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "So he shepherded them according to the integrity of his heart, And guided them by the skillfulness of his hands. "
        }
      ]
